# Valle Studio Salon — Online Reservation & Payment System

## Overview

A full-stack Next.js 14 (App Router) salon booking application for **Valle Studio Salon** covering Hair, Nails, and Brows services. Customers can register or book as guests; an admin dashboard provides full reservation, walk-in, payment, and promotions management. GCash payments are handled via **Xendit API**, and all data/auth is backed by **Supabase**.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Supabase & Xendit credentials** — You will need to supply `.env.local` values for `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`, `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`, and `XENDIT_SECRET_KEY` before the payment and auth flows are fully functional. The scaffold will be wired up but will require these values.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Admin account seeding** — The admin dashboard will be protected by a Supabase `admin` role stored in a `profiles` table. After the DB schema is applied, you will need to manually promote at least one user to admin (or we can seed via a script).

> [!WARNING]
> **Xendit GCash is a Philippine payment method** — Xendit's GCash integration requires a live or sandbox Xendit PH account. Make sure your account is set up for GCash E-Wallet charges before testing.

