### Phase 2 — Supabase Database Schema

#### [NEW] `supabase/migrations/001_initial_schema.sql`

**Tables:**
| Table | Key Columns |
|---|---|
| `profiles` | id (FK auth.users), full_name, phone, role (`customer`/`admin`) |
| `services` | id, name, category (`hair`/`nails`/`brows`), duration_min, price, is_active |
| `promotions` | id, code, discount_type (`percent`/`fixed`), discount_value, valid_from, valid_to, max_uses, uses_count |
| `bookings` | id, profile_id (nullable for guests), guest_name, guest_phone, guest_email, service_id, stylist_name, booking_date, booking_time, status (`pending`/`confirmed`/`completed`/`cancelled`), is_walkin, created_at |
| `payments` | id, booking_id, method (`cash`/`gcash`/`online_gcash`), amount, status (`pending`/`paid`/`failed`), xendit_id, paid_at |
| `promotion_uses` | id, promotion_id, booking_id |

**RLS Policies:**
- Customers can read/create/update their own bookings
- Admins have full CRUD on all tables
- Service and promotion reads are public

