## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Stylist Management** — Should stylists be manageable as users of the system, or just stored as simple name strings? Do customers need to pick a specific stylist during booking?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Booking Slot Duration** — Are all slots 30 minutes, or does it depend on the service duration? For example, a haircut might be 60 min while a nail polish is 30 min.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Multiple Services** — Can a customer book multiple services in one appointment, or only one service per booking?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Email Notifications** — Should booking confirmations be sent via email? (Supabase SMTP or a third-party like Resend/SendGrid)

